nodes.text: Oggem 'Old Ogger' Baobab was explorer Mungo Baobab's great uncle.

Oggem disappeared on the hunt for the fabled roonstones, long before the Clone Wars turned the Galactic Republic into the Galactic Empire. Many years later, he was found by Mungo in a crashed agricultural freighter in Roon's Bantha Graveyard. However, Oggem died shortly after giving his nephew his cache of roonstones.
